{"tid":1307464,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)換命快遞1-3","createTime":"2019-07-11T14:49:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T19:21:53.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3d63a82fe5aa623b098d5eb6249dbb7498d9dc1c","tid":1307464,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T14:49:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=mly3UyGsD7RWnvW57yDWjgX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=5960ff2c\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=mly3UyGsD7RWnvW57yDWjgX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=cf5fb2b5\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=mly3UyGsD7RWnvW57yDWjgX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=a264a928\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/b/b2/The_Transporter_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fb%2Fb2%2FThe_Transporter_Poster.jpg&h=d7227631&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.從特種部隊退休的法蘭克&middot;馬丁，在法國地中海濱用「運輸者」的代號，駕駛BMW自營快遞生意，為各式各樣的委託人完成限時交易。對於工作，法蘭克有一套嚴格的規定：「不改變交易細節」、「不過問雙方姓名」、「不在乎快遞內容」<br />\n<br />\n2.法蘭克&middot;馬丁（傑森&middot;史塔森飾）從法國南部搬遷至美國佛羅里達州邁阿密。出於人情，他暫時擔任有錢人家比令家族的司機。而由於傑佛遜（馬修&middot;摩丁飾）高姿態的政府工作需求，使得他與奧黛麗&middot;比令（琥珀&middot;瓦萊塔飾）的婚姻關係處於高度緊張狀態。法蘭克與比令夫妻就讀小學的兒子傑克（亨特&middot;克拉里飾）相處融洽，並每日駕駛著奧迪A8 W12載他上下學。隨後，稍顯醉意的奧黛麗出現在法蘭克的家中，並且試圖勾引他，但法蘭克機靈地將她送回家<br />\n<br />\n3.一家廢棄物回收商「ECO-CORP」，想要把回收來的有毒廢棄物運至烏克蘭丟棄，卻遭到烏克蘭環保部部長斷然拒絕，於是「ECO-CORP」命令槍手約拿&middot;強生綁架了部長的愛女瓦倫蒂娜，想逼部長就範。強生認為自己運送肉票有危險，於是強迫了法蘭克接下了這個任務，並在法蘭克、瓦倫蒂娜手上綁上了炸彈感應手環，只要他們一離開汽車，他們就會被炸死，法蘭克要怎麼帶著瓦倫蒂娜全面封鎖呢？<br />\n<br />\n11 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  恐怖片黎 好似係<br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=mly3UyGsD7RWnvW57yDWjgX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=bcb1b220\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=mly3UyGsD7RWnvW57yDWjgX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=0a88c89d\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c70797811788de7356a195cab07fa62c03a80e94","tid":1307464,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T14:50:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ede2e70245f490fe7dccb02bd27e1f503db191f","tid":1307464,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T15:04:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/n